# Line-ending policy: LF in the repository AND in every working tree,
# on every platform. sparcli's MinGW/MSYS2 Windows build runs shell scripts
# (tests/cli/*.sh, completions) and a Makefile through /bin/sh - a CRLF
# shebang line breaks the interpreter, and a stray CR leaks into make
# variable values. macOS/Linux already use LF, so this is a no-op there.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be eol-converted.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
